reviewtext: It's a power strip, not really a lot to say.  I got two of these for a very low price.  Monster products are pretty pricy, however if you get them on sale they are well made, attractive looking, and have been reliable so far for me.  I have several surge protector/power strips from Monster (all purchased at steep discounts from list) as well as some cables.  They all work fine, and the ergonomics are very good.
